snippet.title: Best VGM 1959 - Glover - Atlantis Realm, Level 2
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Glover (1998)
Atlantis Realm, Level 2
Rob Lord, Paul Weir & Mark Bandola
